    title: 'Senior Android Developer (f/m/d) (80-100%)',
    description:
      '\u003cp\u003eOur mission at \u003ca href="http://t3u1.mjt.lu/lnk/ANEAAKEj_EcAAAAAAAAAAG3sWXAAAAAA-nQAAAAAAAZPNgBgojaTA1gju6NOSlCaBh4lywAOTAAGCXo/2/Ouq1YFHeabfDMP1oq8rygg/aHR0cDovL3d3dy5taW1pLmlv"\u003eMimi\u003c/a\u003e is to give everyone the best possible hearing experience and protect your hearing health. We are the world’s leading provider of hearing-based audio personalization and digital hearing test technologies.  Our team has developed a biologically-inspired and proprietary audio processing technology that knows how well you hear in order to personalize your listening experience and prevent hearing damage. Mimi’s technology can be integrated into consumer electronics devices, such as headphones, smartphones, TVs, in-flight entertainment systems and a range of systems and platforms.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOur Team\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe are an eclectic bunch of over 60 people of 20 different nationalities — including sound engineers, product designers, researchers, scientists, and software developers, all working together to create a world where hearing ability is no barrier to amazing, personalized sound. At Mimi, diversity is our strength. We\'re based in Berlin — start-up capital of the world, and we’re invested not only in products that help the world hear better, but in people who make our culture smarter, richer, and more human.  We are committed to creating a culture that nourishes personal growth as a basis for company growth. We are a learning organization; we love to work with people who take initiative and are not afraid to try, fail and try again.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThis can be your workplace\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYearly education budgets, flat hierarchies, flexible working environments, regular working from home opportunities, flexible holiday policies and team events... We do what we can to keep our teams engaged and thriving. But, no \'perk\' is more rewarding than the experience of working side by side with a group of brilliant, passionate people creating something meaningful together. We\'re growing fast and always on the lookout to hire talented, driven, and friendly folks, who are ready to meet new challenges and realize new dreams with us.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat you will do\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo help us bring amazing hearing technology to more people around the world, we are looking for a \u003cstrong\u003eSenior Android Developer (f/m/d)\u003c/strong\u003e for employment in Berlin.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNOTE:\u003c/strong\u003e With this role we are happy to support flexible working and accept candidates looking for a working week of 32-40 hours (80-100%)\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs our \u003cstrong\u003eSenior Android Developer (f/m/d)\u003c/strong\u003e you will...\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaintain and develop our Android SDK to deliver sound personalization technologies to partner products\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork closely with your colleagues defining important architectural concepts and API evolution strategies\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDevise ways to improve our Android development ecosystem and processes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProvide partner product integration support\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse Kotlin, Coroutines, ConstraintLayout, Retrofit, Glide and the usual mix of Jetpack libraries in our codebase, with MVVM architecture where required.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat you bring to the table\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e3+ years of experience as a native mobile software developer on Android\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStrong Kotlin skills\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep knowledge and experience with the Android platform and related frameworks\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSolid and well-reasoned software engineering decision making\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCollaborative, curious and team-focused mindset\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFluent in English\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAdditionally it would be great if you have:\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePrior experience developing and supporting SDKs\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA BS/MS degree in computer science, engineering or a related study\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAn interest in audio, music, or sound\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat we offer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA top-caliber, diverse and international team of dedicated domain experts\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA high degree of flexibility in organizing your work and full responsibility for your own projects\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWorking from home opportunities\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe opportunity to make an impact on an untapped market and contribute to the development of a truly innovative product and company\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAn entrepreneurial experience in a young, fast-moving startup located in the heart of trendy Berlin-Friedrichshain\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYearly education budget and a company culture that nourishes personal growth\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eModern working equipment plus plenty of audio perks and cool toys to try out\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWeekly company meals, team-building events and an annual summer trip\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFlexible holiday policy\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMonthly Lieferando credit\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFind out more about us on our website: \u003ca href="http://t3u1.mjt.lu/lnk/ANEAAKEj_EcAAAAAAAAAAG3sWXAAAAAA-nQAAAAAAAZPNgBgojaTA1gju6NOSlCaBh4lywAOTAAGCXo/4/f_D9xYmDqv29JKgYNGWFIg/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubWltaS5pby8"\u003ewww.mimi.io\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDISCLAIMER\nWe know that some people have a tendency not to apply to jobs unless they meet 100% of the requirements. However, if you think that this job is great for you then please, send in your application!\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHOW MIMI ORGANIZES WORK DURING THE SARS-COV-2 PANDEMIC\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe latest relevant information, as well as individual advice, is regularly provided to employees\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeprioritized physical access to Mimi\'s office per official recommendations\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWe provide assistance in equipping your home office (desk, chair, screen, internet connection etc)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWe offer flexible working hours, asynchronous communication.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWe prioritize the well-being of all Mimians by fostering remote personal interaction and professional assistance in dealing with challenging personal situations for example by:\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEncouraging shared virtual lunches and coffees to get to know your colleagues\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOrganizing weekly food delivery services for remote workers\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffering digital counseling sessions with external coaches\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/6c7c813e0d1be10274b75efe081f203514869d9d/68747470733a2f2f742e676f686972696e672e636f6d2f682f65356439646137386463343964316362653930656130343463653334386466373133626132323734633632616233316239373362633264386538396531643537"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n',
